<p>
	A wonderful bath and massage oil all in one with the great relaxing fragrance of top quality fresh lavender essential oil. For a lovely relaxing bath pour a small amount into warm water and mix well before slipping in and floating away with the naturally fragranced water, emerging relaxed and refreshed with a beautiful lavender aroma around you. For massage use a small amount warmed in palms first, keep touch light and sensitive for a relaxing massage helping to calm both mind and body.</p>
